ADDITIONAL DISCLAIMER FOR BLOCKCHAIN DATA:

The pre-computed blockchain data files in this repository (commitment trees,
checksums, manifests) are derived from publicly available Zclassic blockchain
data. This data:

1. Contains NO private keys, seeds, mnemonics, or wallet-specific information
2. Contains NO personally identifiable information
3. Is independently verifiable against any Zclassic full node
4. Is provided for convenience to reduce wallet sync time

The maintainers of this repository:

- Make no warranties about data accuracy or completeness
- Are not responsible for any financial losses from using this data
- Recommend users verify critical data against their own full node
- Provide this data on an "AS IS" basis without any guarantees

USE AT YOUR OWN RISK. Always verify important transactions and balances
using multiple independent sources.
